dct_title_s: Map of a part of the middle portion Muskingum River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. A portion of the Middle of Muskingum River Basin
dct_description_sm: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Scale bar lower right corner of map.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the middle portion of the Muskingum River Basin and quality of underground water.
